This paper discusses resource allocation issues in wireless networks with RF energy harvesting capability, which is a topic related to network infrastructure, communication, and signal processing. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper also discusses information theory and system control, which are related to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also mentions multimedia and augmented reality, which are related to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.AR (Augmented Reality).
